gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 97, Timberwolves 94
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeated the Timberwolves, 97-94.  Dennis Schroder recorded 22 points and seven assists for the Raptors, while O.G. Anunoby added 20 points and six rebounds in the victory.  Anthony Edwards led all scorers with 26 points and 14 rebounds for the Timberwolves in the losing effort.  The Raptors improve to 1-0 on the season, while the Timberwolves fall to 0-1.
